snippet.title: Spirits of Baciu Teaser
snippet.description:
🍂SPIRITS OF BACIU is the enigmatic adventure of The Lost One, a mysterious cat-like spirit who suddenly awakens in the dark Baciu forest. Help him to find his way through the woods, solving puzzles and facing the spirits that inhabit this strange place.

🍃SAVE THE UPCOMING KICKSTARTER CAMPAIGN:https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hornslevelup/spirits-of-baciu
🍃WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2719410/Spirits_of_Baciu/

🍃Follow us to be updated: https://linktr.ee/hornslevelup
